<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset - AFINTHRIVE ADVISORY</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 580px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #1a365d;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 0;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: #1a365d;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .info {
            background: #fef9e7;
            border: 1px solid #f7dc6f;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #856404;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>AFINTHRIVE ADVISORY</h1>
            <p>Password Reset Request</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password for the Afin Advisory Influncer Dashboard.</p>

        <div style="text-align:center; margin:30px 0;">
            <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="btn">Reset Your Password</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info">
            This reset link will expire in <strong>{{expiryHours}} hours</strong>. If you don’t reset your password
            within this time, you’ll need to request a new link.
        </div>

        <p>If you did not request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your account will remain
            secure.</p>

        <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@afinadvisory.com"
                style="color:#1a365d;">info@afinadvisory.com</a></p>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>AFINTHRIVE ADVISORY PRIVATE LIMITED</p>
            <p>402, 4th Floor, City Corporate Tower, Jaipur, Rajasthan, India, 302001.</p>
            <p>©️ 2025 AFINTHRIVE ADVISORY. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>